name: Sci-oly-bungee-drop-2015
tagline: Building a better solution for measuring and comparing results for an excellent Science Olympiad event: Bungee Drop
body:
Integrating physical computing with a beloved Science Olympiad event to create a low-cost solution for data collection. Hopefully bringing data driven solutions to practicing and competition for the event called Bungee Drop. 

Please help us by coding or adding project design ideas in whatever way you can :)
